    fees_en:'- A revenue stamp of 1,000 LBP on each document. - For domestic workers, a fee of 240,000 LBP per year. - Third category: 480,000 LBP. - Second category: 960,000 LBP. - First category: 1,800,000 LBP. Pursuant to the 2002 Budget Law issued on 8/2/2002.',
