    processingTime_en:'About two weeks.',
    steps_en:['The application is submitted to the Sales Directorate, which verifies the availability of the documents and then sets an appointment for the applicant to collect the license if approved.','The application is forwarded through the administrative hierarchy, successively, to the Litigation and Central Control Directorate, and then to the Director General and the Government Commissioner, who review and sign it once the documents are complete and the legal conditions are met.','The application is then returned to the Sales Directorate, which delivers the card to the applicant and files the transaction.'],
