    fees_en:'Revenue stamp of 1,000 LBP.',
    processingTime_en:'Immediately | Immediately | One day | 3-4 days',
    steps_en:['The application is submitted to either:','The registry of the regional department, which forwards it to the head of the department, who approves the application.','The registry of the Directorate of Agricultural Resources, which forwards it to the Director of Agricultural Resources, who refers it to the head of the Horticulture and Field Crops Department, with the signing authority determined according to the number [of saplings].','Up to 25 saplings: the head of the department.','Up to 75 saplings: the Director General.','If the number exceeds 75 saplings: the Minister.'],
    whereToApply_en:'',
